&gt; +=C2=A0 =C2=A0 [command_buffer addCompletedHandler:<br>
&gt; +=C2=A0 =C2=A0 =C2=A0 =C2=A0 ^(id&lt;MTLCommandBuffer&gt; cb)<br>
