gt;mapped_regions-&gt;len);<br>
&gt; +<br>
&gt; +=C2=A0 =C2=A0 =C2=A0 =C2=A0 apple_gfx_destroy_task(s, task);<br>
&gt; +=C2=A0 =C2=A0 };<br>
